law.history: Repealed 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 488, sec. 34, effective July 14, 2000. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 184, secs. 7 and 15. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3990e-12.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Power of cities to regulate brokers not affected.
